        </p>
        -->
        <p>
            <a href="https://finishednotes.com/" title="Podcast website">
                <img class="transform hover:scale-110 transition-all rotate-6 rounded-sm w-24 h-24 lg:w-28 lg:h-28 ml-2 lg:ml-4 float-right" src="/images/aynfy-show-cover-1x.webp" alt="AYNFY Podcast" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            Dr. White is the creator of a podcast by and for counselors, <em>"<a href="https://finishednotes.com/" title="Podcast website">Are Your Notes Finished Yet?</a>" Conversations for today's mental health professionals</em>.
        </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full">
            <ul role="list" class="link-list items-center grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 text-base font-bold leading-4">
                <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <Icon name="icon-mail" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
                    <a href="mailto:counseling@kristicashwhite.net" title="send Kristi an email">Email Kristi</a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <Icon name="icon-linkedin" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
                    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/kristicashwhite" title="send Kristi an email">Follow on LinkedIn</a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-x-3 mb-4">
                    <Icon name="icon-phone" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
                    <a href="tel:503-512-0553" title="Call Kristi">Call Kristi</a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                    <a href="https://kristicashwhitecounseling.clientsecure.me" target="_blank" class="button inline-flex items-center gap-x-1.5 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all" title="Start your visit in a new window">
                        <Icon name="icon-date" class="h-5 w-4 fill-current" />
                        Schedule a visit with Kristi
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
    </section>
    <!-- <section class="social grid "></section> -->
</MainLayout>
